headline: Morgan Stanley Wealth Management Delivers New Tool to Help Clients Tackle Single Stock Risk
summary: NEW YORK, July 24, 2025--Morgan Stanley Wealth Management’s Global Investment Office (GIO) has launched the Equity Vulnerability Score, a proprietary tool that can help clients and the Financial Advisors who serve them measure and rank the susceptibility of US stocks to potential future drops in value.
